extends layout

block content
  section(class="bg-[url('/public/images/close-up-portrait-female-hands-slicing-vegetables.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-center text-white h-screen")
    div(class="h-full backdrop-brightness-[.25]")
      div(class="h-full container mx-auto px-4 xl:px-32 flex flex-col justify-center gap-8")
        h1(class="text-6xl font-bold") Organize your kitchen
        p(class="text-2xl") Kochii assists and encourages individuals for a manageable meal preparation lifestyle
        div(class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 text-center")
          a(class='font-bold rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-white py-4 px-16' href="/signup" role="button") Sign Up
          a(class='font-bold rounded-full text-white border py-4 px-16' href="/#features" role="button") Learn More
      div(class="absolute pb-16 w-full bottom-0 flex justify-center")
        a(href="/#features")
          i(class="bi bi-chevron-compact-down text-6xl")
  div(class="bg-gray-100")
    div(class="container mx-auto px-4 xl:px-32")
      section(class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row mt-[-4rem] gap-8" id="features")
        div(class="flex-1 z-10 bg-white rounded-ss-3xl rounded-ee-3xl shadow-2xl text-center py-16 px-8")
          i(class='bi bi-clipboard-check text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
          h3(class="text-xl font-bold my-4") Record
          p.
            Keep track of what you buy and use on a week-by-week basis and
            organize them using Kochii's simplified user interface.
        div(class="flex-1 z-10 bg-white rounded-ss-3xl rounded-ee-3xl shadow-2xl text-center py-16 px-8")
          i(class='bi bi-bell text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
          h3(class="text-xl font-bold my-4") Notify 
          p.
            Receive real-time up to date notifications regarding the
            status of your inventory with a quick glance.
        div(class="flex-1 z-10 bg-white rounded-ss-3xl rounded-ee-3xl shadow-2xl text-center py-16 px-8")
          i(class='bi bi-bar-chart-line text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
          h3(class="text-xl font-bold my-4") Analyze 
          p.
            Examine a summary of your inventory's current and weekly
            state, and gain insights on your unforeseen behaviors.
      section(class="py-16 flex justify-between")
        div(class="flex-1 text-center")
          h2(class='text-5xl font-light bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text lg:text-left') A mindful approach to consumption
          p(class="my-8 lg:text-left").
            Recognize what you have, purchasing only what you truly need, and reduce waste to 
            not only save money but also minimize your environmental impact.
          div(class="flex flex-col gap-6 justify-center md:flex-row lg:justify-start")
            div(class="")
              i(class='bi bi-book text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
              h3(class="text-xl font-medium mt-4") Find Recipes
            div(class="md:border-x md:px-6")
              i(class='bi bi-bag text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
              h3(class="text-xl font-medium mt-4") Grocery List
            div(class="")
              i(class='bi bi-wallet2 text-6xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text')
              h3(class="text-xl font-medium mt-4") Save Money
          div(class="mt-16 flex flex-col justify-center md:flex-row lg:justify-start")
            a(class='font-bold rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-white py-4 px-12' href="/signup" role="button") Sign Up
        div(class="hidden lg:block flex-1")
          img(class="h-full w-full rounded-ee-3xl" alt="A white grocery bag filled with apples, asparagus, potatoes, and tomatoes" src="/public/images/different-vegetables-textile-bag-beige.png" loading="lazy")
  section(class="container mx-auto px-4 xl:px-32 pt-16 pb-32" id="featured-recipes")
    h2(class="text-4xl font-medium text-center") Share your recipes
    p(class="text-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text text-center mb-16") Whats the best way to cook chicken?
    if latest_posts.length > 0
      div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-white")
        each post, index in latest_posts
          article(class="md:first:col-span-2 md:last:col-span-2 rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden")
            a(style="display: block; height: 100%;" href=post.url)
              img(class="rounded-3xl object-cover w-full h-[20rem] brightness-50 hover:scale-110 hover:brightness-100 duration-200" src=`data:${post.banner.contentType};base64,${post.banner.data.toString('base64')}`)
              div(class="rounded-3xl w-full absolute bottom-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-end pointer-events-none")
                div(class="rounded-3xl py-1 px-4 backdrop-brightness-50")
                  h4(class="text-xl font-extrabold") #{post.title}
                  p Jeffrey Pineda
    else
      p(class="text-center text-2xl") Be the first to share!
  div(class="bg-primary text-white pt-2")
    section(class="bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue lg:bg-[url('/public/images/line-slash.svg')] bg-no-repeat mt-[-4rem] text-center py-8 lg:py-2 lg:bg-75%")
      div(class="container mx-auto px-4 xl:px-32 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 items-center py-6")
        p(class="text-2xl") Always providing the best service
        a(class="font-bold rounded-full bg-white py-4 px-12 text-primary shadow-2xl border" href="#features" role="button") Join Newsletter
    section(class="container mx-auto px-4 xl:px-32 py-16")
      h2(class="text-4xl font-medium text-center mb-16") Who we are
      div(class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8")
        div(class="hidden md:block")
          img(alt="A brown wooden table with a bowl of apples, a bowl of flour, a chopping board, a whisk, and a rolling pin." src="/public/images/andy-chilton-0JFveX0c778-unsplash.png" loading="lazy")
        div(class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2")
          h3(class="text-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text") Who created Kochii?
          p(class="my-4").
            Kochii is a personal open source project created by Jeffrey Ram Pineda as a hobby. 
            It is created with Angular as a frontend framework, Express.js for the backend server, 
            and MongoDB as its database.
          h3(class="text-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-skyblue to-navyblue text-transparent bg-clip-text") What is Kochii?
          p(class="my-4").
            Knowing how to prepare your meals in advance will help you save money. Kochii is designed 
            to keep track of busy people's cooking ingredients with the intention of assisting and 
            promoting home-cooked meals. Through Kochii's upcoming recipe feature, cooking instructions 
            can be archived for later use and will reveal to the user which recipes he/she can and 
            cannot make in relation to his/her recorded inventory.
